; Regression test for issue #1087:
; balance reports incorrect numbers when used with --monthly and/or --average.
;
; When using -M -A (monthly average) with balance, the count used for
; averaging included both original journal postings and synthetic
; period-summary postings generated by interval_posts, inflating the
; divisor and producing incorrect averages.

2014/09/05 test
    A:B   60
    A:A

2014/10/05 test
    A:B    60
    A:A

test -M -A bal A:B
                  60  A:B
end test
